HOw  TO CONNECT TO MYSQL DATABASE FROM VISUALCODE AND FETCH THE DATA

open project in VS Code 
than download package ---
== right-click your project, choose Manage NuGet Packagesâ€¦, in the Search box enter MySqlConnector, and install the package in your project.
dotnet add package MySqlConnector --version 2.2.6

and also download other three extensions---
Install-package Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration;
